            <div type="apparatus">
                <listApp>
                    <app><note>Text after autopsy</note></app>
                    <app loc="4"><note>Bivona (1994) records a triangular interpunct at the beginning of line 4. Autopsy reveals it is a hedera, comparable (although higher on the line) with the hedera later in the same line.</note></app>
                </listApp>
